=> Assumptions: Single currency (₹), simple products, no card payment.
=> Edge Cases: Insufficient funds, out of stock, cancel transaction, no change available.

2. Identify entities and relationships

=> Main entities: VendingMachine, Product, Inventory, Coin, Transaction
=> Key relationships :
VendingMachine has Inventory of Products
Transaction tracks inserted money and selected product

